#FieldworkFriday: the high #Arctic is very remote, so research & teaching are pricey & difficult. A new web-based interface, Svalbox, shares hi-res digital outcrop models w/ relevant public-domain geoscientific datasets for pre, during, & post fieldwork. https://t.co/ePC2n3UGRm https://t.co/NqZMa2cZ9t
Key takeaways: Know your audience. Don't be afraid to say "I don't know, I'll look it up and get back to you." Be true to yourself and your demographic when communicating. #SciComm
